2. DESCRIPTION
--------------

pBot is a modular IRC Bot coded in Perl that can perform many helpful
tasks to make everyday irc'ing easier or fun.

ATTENTION: By using this software, you are stating
that you have read and agreed to the terms in LICENSE.

3. INSTALLATION
---------------

See docs/INSTALL for information on how to install pBot

4. GETTING SUPPORT
------------------

Should you need any help with pBot, please drop by
our IRC chatroom:

Host: irc.connecttek.net
Port: 6667 | SSL: 6697
Channel: #fml


5. REPORTING BUGS
-----------------

Should you come across a bug within the original code, please
report it to us by visiting our IRC ChatRoom stated above